Iniciar projeto

>> npx react-native init myproject

rodar o bundle
>>npx react-native run-android
>> react-native start

Configurando o ambiente
instale o editorConfig
Instalar o eslint
>> yarn add eslint prettier eslint-config-prettier eslint-plugin-prettier babel-eslint -D
>> npm install eslint-plugin-react@latest --save-dev
>>yarn eslint --init
>> yarn
>>yarn add prettier eslint-config-prettier eslint-plugin-prettier babel-eslint -D
**caso ocorra erros**
>>yarn react-native start --reset-cache ou
>> yarn react-native run-android


Intalação do Reactotron
Faça o download e instale
>> yarn add reactotron-react-native

Lidando com navegação
>>yarn add react-navigation react-native-gesture-handler react-native-reanimated

Instalar StyledComponent
>> yarn add styled-components

Utilizar Icons
>> yarn add react-native-vector-icons
>> react-native link react-native-vector-icons
